Battle of the AWD titans. Both the Evo and the GTR have made a career of embarrassing supercars and the like for decades. But when one is built for street cruising, and another built for all-out time attack, which one will emerge victorious?

It’s your LAST CHANCE to score a custom-built Subaru WRX STI and $20,000 cash. Support Team Rubicon and Feeding America and ENTER: http://bit.ly/Last-Chance-Subaru-20K

